# CODEOWNERS - Risk-based review routing
# Changes to these paths require review from the specified teams/individuals
# Used by the complexity classifier for auto-escalation to CRITICAL tier

# Critical paths (auto-escalate to CRITICAL tier)
# /src/auth/           @security-team
# /src/payments/       @security-team
# /migrations/         @db-admin
# /.github/workflows/  @devops-lead
# /constitution.yml    @framework-maintainer

# Standard paths
# /src/                @dev-team
# /tests/              @dev-team
# /docs/               @dev-team
